\lim_{a\to\infty}\left(\int^a_{-a}e^{-x^2}dx\right)^2=\lim_{a\to\infty}\dfrac{1}{4}\pi\left(\operatorname{erf}(a)^2+\operatorname{erf}(-a)^2-2\operatorname{erf}(a)\operatorname{erf}(-a)\right)=\\ \dfrac{\pi}{4}(1+1-(-2))=\pi
